                <div dir="ltr"><font face="verdana, sans-serif"
                    color="#000000"><br>
                  </font></div>
                <div><font face="verdana, sans-serif" color="#000000">As
                    we stand together to fight this pandemic, we want to
                    provide <u>an option</u> to all outstation employees
                    of working from home until December 2020 subject to
                    them being in a <u>work-fit environment</u> (connectivity
                    &amp; availability) and no corner case including
                    infrastructure issues or client issues that require
                    them to come to the office.</font></div>
                <div><font face="verdana, sans-serif" color="#000000"><br>
                  </font></div>
                <div><font face="verdana, sans-serif" color="#000000">Whenever
                    the situation is normalised and local authorities
                    approve 80-100% occupancy for companies. We will
                    open in a safe and secure environment in a phased
                    manner. Then, the preference of returning to office
                    will be given to employees local to Indore. </font></div>
                <div><font face="verdana, sans-serif" color="#000000"><br>
                  </font></div>
                <div><font face="verdana, sans-serif" color="#000000">All
                    this is to ensure safety and well-being of all
                    employees. We hope to keep in mind factors like mode
                    of travel (public/personal) , distance to Indore,
                    containment zones across India, growth in cases etc
                    when returning to office. </font></div>
                <div><font face="verdana, sans-serif" color="#000000"><br>
                  </font></div>
